In the event of an emergency involving anhydrous ammonia, it is our policy to notify the local fire department and the Massac LEPC.

6. Safety improvement is an on-going process at the facility.  Periodic evaluations are performed to assess the maintenance of safe conditions.  There are no specific safety recommendation for implementation at this time.
